    "questionText": "<p>Among the statements :</p>\n<p>(S1) : $$2023^{2022}-1999^{2022}$$ is divisible by 8</p>\n<p>(S2) : $$13(13)^{n}-12 n-13$$ is divisible by 144 for infinitely many $$n \\in \\mathbb{N}$$</p>",
